abstract: >-
  deepEMIA is a comprehensive deep learning toolkit for electron microscopy
  and scientific image analysis. It provides a robust pipeline for dataset
  preparation, model training, hyperparameter optimization, evaluation,
  scalable inference with tile-based processing and model ensemble, and
  automated measurement extraction including area, perimeter, axes,
  circularity, and wavelength measurements.
